#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an4.255"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.255:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.255:0.2"
msgid "26. Abhiññāvagga "
msgstr "26. Insight "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.255:0.3"
msgid "255. Pariyesanāsutta "
msgstr "255. Searches "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an4.255:1.1"
msgid "“Catasso imā, bhikkhave, anariyapariyesanā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these four ignoble searches. "

msgctxt "an4.255:1.2"
msgid "Katamā catasso? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "an4.255:1.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco attanā jarādhammo samāno jarādhammaṃyeva pariyesati; "
msgstr "Someone liable to grow old searches only for what grows old. "

msgctxt "an4.255:1.4"
msgid "attanā byādhidhammo samāno byādhidhammaṃyeva pariyesati; "
msgstr "Someone liable to sickness searches only for what gets sick. "

msgctxt "an4.255:1.5"
msgid "attanā maraṇadhammo samāno maraṇadhammaṃyeva pariyesati; "
msgstr "Someone liable to death searches only for what dies. "

msgctxt "an4.255:1.6"
msgid "attanā saṅkilesadhammo samāno saṅkilesadhammaṃyeva pariyesati. "
msgstr "Someone whose nature is defiled searches only for what is defiled. "

msgctxt "an4.255:1.7"
msgid "Imā kho, bhikkhave, catasso anariyapariyesanā. "
msgstr "These are the four ignoble searches. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.248, sc2
msgctxt "an4.255:2.1"
msgid "Catasso imā, bhikkhave, ariyapariyesanā. "
msgstr "There are these four noble searches. "

msgctxt "an4.255:2.2"
msgid "Katamā catasso? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "an4.255:2.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco attanā jarādhammo samāno jarādhamme ādīnavaṃ viditvā ajaraṃ anuttaraṃ yogakkhemaṃ nibbānaṃ pariyesati; "
msgstr "Someone who is liable to grow old, knowing the drawback in what grows old, searches for the unaging supreme sanctuary, extinguishment. "

msgctxt "an4.255:2.4"
msgid "attanā byādhidhammo samāno byādhidhamme ādīnavaṃ viditvā abyādhiṃ anuttaraṃ yogakkhemaṃ nibbānaṃ pariyesati; "
msgstr "Someone who is liable to get sick, knowing the drawback in what gets sick, searches for the sickness-free supreme sanctuary, extinguishment. "

msgctxt "an4.255:2.5"
msgid "attanā maraṇadhammo samāno maraṇadhamme ādīnavaṃ viditvā amataṃ anuttaraṃ yogakkhemaṃ nibbānaṃ pariyesati; "
msgstr "Someone who is liable to die, knowing the drawback in what dies, searches for the deathless supreme sanctuary, extinguishment. "

msgctxt "an4.255:2.6"
msgid "attanā saṅkilesadhammo samāno saṅkilesadhamme ādīnavaṃ viditvā asaṅkiliṭṭhaṃ anuttaraṃ yogakkhemaṃ nibbānaṃ pariyesati. "
msgstr "Someone whose nature is defiled, knowing the drawback in what is defiled, searches for the undefiled supreme sanctuary, extinguishment. "

msgctxt "an4.255:2.7"
msgid "Imā kho, bhikkhave, catasso ariyapariyesanā”ti. "
msgstr "These are the four noble searches.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.255:2.8"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

